00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Here's what science actually says about chronic inflammation.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,400
Chronic inflammation is your body's silent alarm system.

3
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:10,400
It's meant to protect but can spiral out of control.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:16,400
When it persists, it can contribute to diseases like heart disease, diabetes, and even cancer.

5
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:21,600
Studies show a connection between chronic inflammation and genetics, diet, and lifestyle choices.

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:26,800
But here’s the twist: recent research suggests that not all inflammation is bad.

7
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,000
It's about balance.

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Understanding your body's signals can guide you towards better health.

